Use graphics.
Use input.

Call create window with 1280, 720.

Let running be true.
Let quit be false.

Let x be 400.
Let y be 300.

While running is true, repeat.
    Set quit to the result of calling check events.
    If quit is true, then.
        Set running to false.
    End If.

    Call set background with 30, 40, 40.

    Call update display.
    Call wait with 16.
End while.

Call close window.
